text: Renata Carraretto (born 27 October 1923) was an Italian alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Italian female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Italy Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Cortina d'Ampezzo
